WEBVTT

00:12.910 --> 00:15.510
The conflict between Li and Wei
has become chaotic.

00:15.510 --> 00:18.770
And you intend to establish
your own faction in the future.

00:19.320 --> 00:22.320
Do you wish to make this chaos even worse?

00:35.110 --> 00:36.030
As a man,

00:37.100 --> 00:39.030
one must not be a fence-sitter.

00:40.170 --> 00:41.360
As a minister,

00:42.600 --> 00:44.800
one must not switch sides frivolously.

00:46.530 --> 00:48.000
That is all I have to say.

00:49.590 --> 00:51.980
Zheng! Zheng!

00:52.520 --> 00:53.710
Are you here?

00:54.880 --> 00:58.600
Zheng, Mrs. Zhao
asked you to go back for lunch.

01:05.129 --> 01:07.990
Young lady, why don't you
come in and sit for a while?

01:08.720 --> 01:11.880
I'm not going into a villain's house.

01:11.910 --> 01:13.530
Thank you, Mr. Scholar.

01:13.870 --> 01:15.530
Why do you call me Mr. Scholar?

01:15.920 --> 01:19.830
My sister said your carriage
was full of books.

01:22.210 --> 01:24.140
I won't disturb your rest, My Lord.

01:25.510 --> 01:27.850
Please pretend I was never here.

01:33.880 --> 01:34.410
Let's go.

02:19.840 --> 02:22.400
Was that man really the Marquis of Wu'an?

02:29.470 --> 02:31.000
He just broke a cup. So what?

02:31.910 --> 02:34.260
The Marquis of Wu'an is nothing special.

02:39.680 --> 02:42.550
His skills seem to have been improving.

04:11.320 --> 04:15.940
[Pursuit of Jade]

04:16.010 --> 04:18.620
[Episode 11]

04:25.650 --> 04:26.640
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

04:37.120 --> 04:37.950
Changyu!

04:39.360 --> 04:40.240
Qianqian?

04:40.240 --> 04:42.890
Which young lady has been doing dirty,
exhausting work all day

04:42.890 --> 04:44.290
yet is still this pretty?

04:44.720 --> 04:46.270
Hop on. I'll take you home.

04:47.000 --> 04:48.720
No need. I'll go back myself.

04:48.720 --> 04:50.560
Usually, I'd let you be,

04:50.560 --> 04:51.800
but today I kept you here late

04:51.800 --> 04:53.120
because there were too many banquets.

04:53.120 --> 04:54.070
It's already dark.

04:54.070 --> 04:56.600
I'm worried about you
walking alone at night.

04:57.270 --> 04:58.040
Get in.

04:59.600 --> 05:01.800
It's okay. I can manage it alone.
You go.

05:02.040 --> 05:03.240
Well then, thank you.

05:13.200 --> 05:15.620
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

05:30.190 --> 05:30.920
Come out.

05:34.310 --> 05:34.920
Your Lordship.

05:34.640 --> 05:37.920
[Xie Wu, Blood-Robed Cavalry Guard]
[Xie Qi, Blood-Robed Cavalry Guard]

05:34.940 --> 05:35.800
Your Lordship,

05:36.070 --> 05:37.240
we are late.

05:41.800 --> 05:42.670
You may rise.

05:44.980 --> 05:46.110
How many of you came?

05:47.080 --> 05:48.280
Just Xie Qi and me.

05:48.540 --> 05:49.480
We were afraid of being noticed,

05:49.480 --> 05:50.950
so we didn't bring the other guards along.

05:50.950 --> 05:53.280
Your Lordship, fortunately you are safe.

05:54.830 --> 05:56.690
Unfortunately, Xie Yi and Xie San

05:57.520 --> 05:58.950
died because of me.

06:01.950 --> 06:03.290
We brothers once swore

06:03.360 --> 06:04.360
to keep you safe

06:04.510 --> 06:06.110
even at the cost of our lives.

06:08.160 --> 06:09.560
No one from the Xie family

06:10.130 --> 06:11.640
would die in vain.

06:12.160 --> 06:14.450
All of us are hoping you return soon.

06:14.630 --> 06:17.430
That Wei Xuan
is running rampant in the army.

06:18.300 --> 06:20.740
He flaunts his power every day.

06:21.190 --> 06:22.730
The brothers can hardly wait to tie him up

06:22.730 --> 06:24.040
and throw him to the wolves.

06:24.040 --> 06:24.830
Let him be.

06:27.160 --> 06:28.480
Before long, a bloody battle

06:28.480 --> 06:31.810
between us and Prince Changxin
in Chongzhou is inevitable.

06:31.950 --> 06:34.190
Storing grain
is the top priority right now.

06:34.190 --> 06:35.830
The Court refuses to release grain.

06:35.830 --> 06:37.680
Wei Xuan has accepted Prime Minister Wei's
military order

06:37.680 --> 06:39.940
and plans to requisition grain locally.

06:45.390 --> 06:46.470
Sixteen years ago,

06:47.240 --> 06:49.170
it was in Jinzhou where the Xie Army

06:49.650 --> 06:53.310
suffered a crushing defeat due to
lack of provisions and support.

06:54.960 --> 06:57.490
I absolutely cannot
repeat the same mistake.

06:59.630 --> 07:01.680
Wei Xuan is ambitious
for great achievements.

07:01.680 --> 07:04.430
It's only a matter of time
before he loses to Prince Changxin.

07:04.430 --> 07:05.890
Let's just go with the flow

07:06.040 --> 07:07.720
and let Wei Xuan
and those idiots under his command

07:07.720 --> 07:08.630
serve as bait

07:09.480 --> 07:11.720
to lure Prince Changxin
to lead troops south.

07:11.720 --> 07:13.870
By then, I will have my own strategy.

07:14.510 --> 07:17.770
So, Your Lordship, you don't plan
to return to camp for now?

07:19.400 --> 07:20.520
You go back first

07:21.000 --> 07:22.680
and spread the news of my death.

07:22.680 --> 07:24.540
The more people know, the better.

07:24.720 --> 07:25.390
Yes.

07:33.190 --> 07:33.830
Go now.

07:34.080 --> 07:34.690
Yes.

07:43.290 --> 07:45.240
The braised pork is sold out today.

07:45.390 --> 07:47.159
The pig head meat was very popular.

07:47.159 --> 07:47.800
Really?

07:48.600 --> 07:51.590
A few days ago, Mrs. Wang said
her daughter is getting married

07:51.590 --> 07:53.430
and ordered half a side of pork from me.

07:53.430 --> 07:55.290
Won't that mean more work for you?

07:55.630 --> 07:57.480
I welcome this kind of work.

08:02.300 --> 08:04.200
Who is it? Who are you?

08:07.950 --> 08:09.410
I'll go out and take a look.

08:23.950 --> 08:26.000
Qianqian, don't come out now.

08:26.510 --> 08:27.870
I'll deal with them.

08:27.950 --> 08:28.630
Beat her.

08:40.840 --> 08:42.039
Who sent you?

08:42.440 --> 08:43.360
Was it him?

08:43.380 --> 08:45.780
Why won't he let me go
after all these years?

08:50.480 --> 08:53.320
Help! Help!

09:05.960 --> 09:07.090
Changyu, watch out!

09:13.750 --> 09:15.550
Don't run!

09:15.840 --> 09:17.630
This voice sounds familiar.

09:20.890 --> 09:21.980
Butcher Guo.

09:22.360 --> 09:23.320
Butcher Guo?

09:24.200 --> 09:25.080
Mrs. Fan...

09:25.600 --> 09:26.440
Heroine Fan.

09:26.910 --> 09:28.040
Mommy!

09:28.600 --> 09:29.790
I just lost my mind for a moment.

09:29.790 --> 09:31.670
You've gone against me time and again.

09:31.670 --> 09:33.480
That doesn't look like losing your mind
for a moment.

09:33.480 --> 09:35.030
Someone paid us

09:35.030 --> 09:36.240
to kill you.

09:38.200 --> 09:38.750
Who?

09:39.080 --> 09:39.750
Who?

09:39.790 --> 09:40.480
Who?

09:42.600 --> 09:43.320
Who!

09:43.960 --> 09:44.720
Changyu!

09:48.670 --> 09:49.630
Since we're selling one,

09:49.630 --> 09:51.030
we might as well sell two!

09:58.750 --> 10:00.110
Go to hell!

10:00.270 --> 10:02.910
Bastard! Come at me if you have the guts!

10:04.510 --> 10:06.240
I'll come at you then!

10:06.320 --> 10:07.120
Changyu!

10:08.510 --> 10:09.030
I...

10:18.330 --> 10:20.280
Changyu! Changyu?

10:23.820 --> 10:24.950
Are you okay?

10:36.090 --> 10:38.730
[Xigu Lane]

10:40.050 --> 10:42.400
Yan Zheng, did you see Changyu?

10:43.350 --> 10:44.480
What's happening here?

10:44.480 --> 10:46.720
-She was drugged. Go get some water.
-Okay.

10:46.720 --> 10:48.230
Honey, come help.

10:48.750 --> 10:50.080
Hello, sir. Hello, sir.

11:03.450 --> 11:04.900
What's happening here?

11:07.100 --> 11:08.060
What?

11:08.150 --> 11:09.980
My butt... hurts.

11:10.030 --> 11:10.910
Hurts?

11:10.960 --> 11:11.870
Where does it hurt?

11:11.870 --> 11:13.050
My butt!

11:13.080 --> 11:13.840
Your butt what?

11:13.840 --> 11:15.320
My butt hurts!

11:15.440 --> 11:17.170
Why hasn't the pain killed you?

11:29.480 --> 11:30.850
Despicable man!

11:33.630 --> 11:34.560
Please spare me.

11:34.600 --> 11:35.840
Please spare me!

11:35.840 --> 11:38.000
I'm not a bandit from Qingfeng Stronghold.

11:38.000 --> 11:41.030
I was bullied by those two broads—

11:41.710 --> 11:42.280
no—

11:42.790 --> 11:44.080
those two ladies from Yixiang Restaurant.

11:44.080 --> 11:46.390
I just wanted to scare them.

11:49.480 --> 11:50.440
Guo!

11:50.720 --> 11:52.510
You took your grudge against Fan Erniu

11:52.510 --> 11:54.550
out on this poor orphan girl?

11:54.570 --> 11:55.840
Are you even human?

11:55.840 --> 11:56.600
My butt...

11:56.620 --> 11:58.200
Say no more.

11:58.200 --> 12:00.320
Do you think the fire isn't big enough?

12:00.320 --> 12:02.600
Do you want to blow the roof off?

12:04.080 --> 12:05.320
It hurts!

12:12.030 --> 12:13.090
Just to scare them?

12:14.080 --> 12:15.750
Didn't you drug her?

12:16.750 --> 12:18.240
What exactly did you want?

12:19.790 --> 12:22.200
I wanted to knock them out first...

12:26.440 --> 12:27.240
And then?

12:32.510 --> 12:33.240
Speak!

12:34.440 --> 12:36.480
Then destroy her meridians...

12:40.200 --> 12:40.960
Is that all?

12:47.170 --> 12:49.120
And sell her to the mountains...

13:01.630 --> 13:02.510
Stop!

13:03.630 --> 13:04.630
Yan, doing this

13:05.070 --> 13:06.600
will only dirty your hands.

13:06.990 --> 13:08.080
How he should be punished

13:08.080 --> 13:09.090
is for the authorities to decide.

13:09.090 --> 13:12.100
The authorities?
If I hadn't been here today,

13:12.480 --> 13:14.750
something bad would have happened
to Changyu.

13:14.750 --> 13:17.600
If you accept your fate, who can save you?

13:19.440 --> 13:20.670
I will take

13:21.440 --> 13:22.680
my own revenge!

13:24.480 --> 13:25.080
Stop!

13:25.080 --> 13:25.600
No!

13:25.720 --> 13:26.480
Yan Zheng!

13:32.240 --> 13:33.120
Don't kill him.

13:33.790 --> 13:34.790
It's not worth it.

13:51.080 --> 13:51.960
Are you okay?

13:53.270 --> 13:53.960
Lie down.

13:58.150 --> 13:59.480
Rest assured and sleep.

13:59.760 --> 14:00.730
I won't kill him.

14:11.670 --> 14:14.050
Alright, don't cry.

14:15.200 --> 14:16.770
I have plenty of strength.

14:16.800 --> 14:17.510
Look.

14:18.510 --> 14:19.600
My hands are fine,

14:19.600 --> 14:20.930
and my feet are fine too.

14:21.150 --> 14:21.880
Stop crying.

14:27.870 --> 14:29.080
Changyu...

14:33.440 --> 14:35.570
Help me get a basin of warm water, okay?

14:36.960 --> 14:37.840
Okay.

14:53.200 --> 14:55.390
How is it? Does your head still hurt?

14:56.750 --> 14:59.550
Do you feel uncomfortable anywhere else?

15:01.480 --> 15:03.210
If you had killed someone for me

15:03.970 --> 15:05.040
and gone to prison,

15:07.140 --> 15:08.600
my head would really hurt.

15:25.200 --> 15:26.080
Promise me.

15:27.440 --> 15:28.770
Don't get into trouble.

15:35.080 --> 15:35.910
Don't worry.

15:37.960 --> 15:39.290
I'll be fine.

15:53.250 --> 15:56.300
Manager, the doors and windows are locked.

15:57.030 --> 15:59.040
The water vats for fire are full.

16:00.080 --> 16:01.290
And I've assigned the boys

16:01.290 --> 16:03.490
to take shifts to guard every two hours.

16:03.670 --> 16:05.270
Do you have any other orders?

16:07.130 --> 16:11.080
Manager, is there going to be a war?

16:13.640 --> 16:16.770
Add 2 more locks tomorrow.

16:17.270 --> 16:19.590
There are already 3 locks on 2 doors.

16:19.670 --> 16:21.440
You still want to add more?

16:21.870 --> 16:22.480
Yes.

16:23.150 --> 16:24.210
Add one more layer,

16:24.790 --> 16:27.920
and reinforce the door frames with iron.

16:29.030 --> 16:29.750
Okay.

17:47.820 --> 17:48.490
Mom.

17:48.970 --> 17:50.570
Were you good today, Bao'er?

17:50.810 --> 17:51.840
Very good.

17:52.100 --> 17:53.460
I didn't go out at all.

17:53.880 --> 17:57.210
I finished
all the homework you left for me.

17:58.530 --> 17:59.730
Such a good boy?

18:00.550 --> 18:03.200
Let's be this good tomorrow too, okay?

18:14.620 --> 18:16.720
[Luyuan]

18:44.160 --> 18:44.960
Great move!

18:44.960 --> 18:45.510
Great...

18:48.680 --> 18:50.790
An Xu, so you know how to play Go?

18:51.590 --> 18:52.680
Just a little.

18:54.110 --> 18:56.310
How about playing a round with me?

18:56.310 --> 18:56.960
Sure.

18:59.240 --> 18:59.850
Alright.

19:11.030 --> 19:12.230
That was satisfying!

19:12.560 --> 19:14.560
Let's play another round tomorrow.

19:15.000 --> 19:15.640
Okay.

19:17.680 --> 19:18.410
Headmaster.

19:23.200 --> 19:26.070
When I was young,
I read a fragment of a Go manual

19:26.550 --> 19:28.080
called "The Mystery of Qi."

19:28.310 --> 19:30.960
I heard that your Library
has over 10,000 books.

19:30.960 --> 19:32.200
I wanted to find it,

19:32.720 --> 19:34.380
but I haven't been able to yet.

19:35.110 --> 19:36.200
This book

19:36.310 --> 19:37.960
is indeed not in the Library.

19:39.440 --> 19:40.160
However,

19:40.640 --> 19:42.310
in the Gongsun family's collection,

19:42.310 --> 19:44.370
there is actually a complete volume.

19:44.680 --> 19:47.110
Unfortunately,
it is my grandfather's treasure

19:47.110 --> 19:48.370
and cannot be lent out.

19:53.280 --> 19:54.790
A gentleman
does not take what others love.

19:54.790 --> 19:56.240
It is natural for Old Mr. Gongsun

19:56.240 --> 19:57.500
to cherish treasures.

20:01.790 --> 20:02.720
However...

20:04.600 --> 20:06.880
Although it cannot be lent out,

20:07.790 --> 20:09.610
I can copy the fragment of the Go manual

20:09.610 --> 20:11.050
and give it to you.

20:12.640 --> 20:13.570
Thank you, Headmaster.

20:13.570 --> 20:22.400
[Penetration and Subtlety]

20:29.640 --> 20:30.630
A ruler

20:30.790 --> 20:34.450
should bear the responsibility
of protecting the common people.

20:54.030 --> 20:56.350
Consort Dowager An,

20:56.720 --> 20:58.580
our new student An Xu

20:58.960 --> 21:01.420
is actually the Princess Royal
in disguise.

21:01.550 --> 21:02.980
I have noticed this

21:03.030 --> 21:04.400
and dare not keep it hidden.

21:04.400 --> 21:07.060
I report it
for Your Highness's consideration.

21:08.280 --> 21:10.280
[Yixiang Restaurant]

21:15.350 --> 21:16.160
Qianqian?

21:17.550 --> 21:18.270
Qianqian?

21:28.660 --> 21:29.510
Where is she?

21:46.990 --> 21:47.710
Changyu.

21:49.110 --> 21:50.550
You scared me.

21:50.570 --> 21:51.770
You asked me to come,

21:51.800 --> 21:52.790
but you weren't here.

21:52.790 --> 21:54.120
I was about to leave.

21:54.710 --> 21:55.670
Go sit down.

22:04.920 --> 22:06.250
Are you feeling better?

22:06.270 --> 22:07.550
I'm fine.

22:07.790 --> 22:09.750
You sent me medicine and food.

22:09.750 --> 22:11.150
I've even gained weight.

22:12.590 --> 22:13.390
How about you?

22:14.160 --> 22:16.510
Were you scared that night?

22:17.370 --> 22:18.370
If you're afraid,

22:18.400 --> 22:19.480
you can tell me.

22:19.680 --> 22:20.860
Don't bottle it up.

22:21.030 --> 22:22.200
It was nothing.

22:22.200 --> 22:23.350
I've seen it all.

22:23.830 --> 22:25.200
Just because a bad guy scared me
with a stick,

22:25.200 --> 22:27.530
does that mean
I should be scared to death?

22:27.920 --> 22:29.740
But your husband...

22:29.880 --> 22:31.540
He was quite scary that night.

22:31.680 --> 22:33.210
He's not usually like that.

22:33.950 --> 22:36.110
He just can't stand anyone hurting me.

22:36.480 --> 22:38.000
I know.

22:38.000 --> 22:39.260
You two love each other,

22:39.260 --> 22:40.990
and it makes everyone jealous.

22:41.030 --> 22:41.640
By the way,

22:42.440 --> 22:43.240
look at this.

22:43.550 --> 22:44.720
Times are chaotic now.

22:44.720 --> 22:46.720
We must learn to protect ourselves.

22:51.880 --> 22:53.920
What is this?

22:54.070 --> 22:55.270
Cornel water.

22:55.790 --> 22:57.590
I got a bigger bottle this time.

22:57.640 --> 22:59.160
Last time it ran out at a critical moment.

22:59.160 --> 23:00.420
This should be enough.

23:00.480 --> 23:02.010
If sprayed in the eyes, it causes
swelling, pain,

23:02.010 --> 23:04.010
and temporary blindness for 3 days.

23:04.380 --> 23:06.840
I didn't know cornel
could be used like that.

23:07.550 --> 23:10.000
Is this what you used on Butcher Guo?

23:11.270 --> 23:12.790
If that's the case,

23:13.160 --> 23:16.400
garlic, ginger,
and peppercorns could work too.

23:19.720 --> 23:21.160
That Guo got off easy.

23:36.310 --> 23:37.040
Headmaster?

23:42.480 --> 23:44.510
I remember someone playing Go with me

23:44.510 --> 23:47.300
from a distance in the Fengyu Pavilion.

23:47.920 --> 23:51.720
Our moves went back and forth,
breaking stalemates again and again.

23:52.310 --> 23:54.350
Who is playing Go here?

23:54.920 --> 23:57.510
Looks like the game isn't over.

24:04.880 --> 24:05.960
I'll place it here.

24:07.790 --> 24:08.510
Is that so?

24:10.030 --> 24:12.560
That was really a meeting
of kindred spirits.

24:15.000 --> 24:16.800
Another white piece was placed!

24:17.350 --> 24:18.200
Look.

24:20.540 --> 24:21.630
Your Highness,

24:21.650 --> 24:23.850
I think someone is inviting you to play.

24:24.570 --> 24:27.230
I'm the one who intruded
on someone else's game.

24:30.110 --> 24:31.680
I also have a friend

24:31.680 --> 24:32.940
who is excellent at Go.

24:33.750 --> 24:34.550
But...

24:35.440 --> 24:36.790
we've never met.

24:37.920 --> 24:39.050
What a coincidence.

24:39.320 --> 24:41.180
Go reveals a gentleman's virtue.

24:41.510 --> 24:43.580
Although I haven't seen my opponent,

24:44.200 --> 24:47.150
I can glimpse his thoughts
through the game.

24:47.310 --> 24:50.040
Playing remotely
is like having a conversation.

24:50.800 --> 24:51.770
It's all about

24:52.200 --> 24:53.750
that moment of connection.

25:16.510 --> 25:18.270
How do I compare

25:19.030 --> 25:19.890
to your friend?

25:23.160 --> 25:26.440
Although we haven't met,

25:27.330 --> 25:29.460
your Go skills are better than theirs.

25:31.880 --> 25:34.270
Once I get your "The Mystery of Qi",

25:34.510 --> 25:36.570
my skills will improve even further.

25:40.160 --> 25:41.070
Perhaps...

25:42.240 --> 25:44.000
I'll be able to meet him soon.

25:47.240 --> 25:48.310
In that case,

25:48.680 --> 25:49.960
when you meet,

25:50.350 --> 25:52.480
you must play a game together.

25:54.400 --> 25:55.200
Young Master!

25:55.440 --> 25:57.840
Y-Young Master! Someone from home is here.

25:59.130 --> 25:59.890
Home?

26:08.270 --> 26:09.790
Your Highness.

26:12.270 --> 26:16.400
I have been ordered
to ask you to return to the palace.

26:44.390 --> 26:47.930
[Seeking Truth in the Classics]

26:45.350 --> 26:47.810
I don't know how
the Consort Dowager learned

26:48.000 --> 26:50.200
that you swapped identities with Mr. An

26:50.440 --> 26:52.240
and came to study at Luyuan Academy.

26:52.240 --> 26:53.370
What did Mother say?

26:54.960 --> 26:57.890
Her Highness has confined Mr. An.

26:58.350 --> 27:00.830
She's furious about this.

27:01.000 --> 27:03.830
She originally allowed you
to return to the Capital next month,

27:03.830 --> 27:06.560
but now you'll have to return
to the palace today.

27:08.940 --> 27:10.670
Your Highness.

27:10.990 --> 27:14.090
I've had people seal the backyard.

27:14.400 --> 27:17.160
No one will notice your departure.

27:17.680 --> 27:22.530
The academy will claim An Xu withdrew
for personal reasons.

27:22.750 --> 27:24.920
This will save everyone's face.

27:25.790 --> 27:27.480
You are thorough, Nanny.

27:28.790 --> 27:30.650
I apologize for my incompetence.

27:30.720 --> 27:33.240
Your Highness, please.

27:39.720 --> 27:40.510
Master,

27:41.660 --> 27:42.990
for the past half month,

27:43.530 --> 27:45.730
have you been the one playing Go with me?

27:46.090 --> 27:48.070
I did not expect that

27:48.210 --> 27:50.040
the one playing chess here every day

27:50.040 --> 27:52.130
would be a lady.

27:56.590 --> 27:57.400
Right.

27:58.440 --> 28:00.640
Those who
can be in Guangling Temple every day

28:00.640 --> 28:02.700
could only be the monks of the temple.

28:04.070 --> 28:05.400
I overthought it.

28:11.910 --> 28:14.910
To play Go remotely in this pavilion

28:14.960 --> 28:17.960
implies a destined bond.

28:17.960 --> 28:21.400
Gongsun, why sever this connection?

28:22.550 --> 28:24.440
I am but a carefree idler,

28:24.440 --> 28:25.770
with nothing to my name.

28:26.310 --> 28:28.370
How could I dare to hold up such a lady?

28:30.110 --> 28:33.010
It was fine
when I didn't know she was a girl.

28:33.400 --> 28:34.790
But now that I know,

28:35.310 --> 28:37.770
it would be improper
to disturb her further.

28:39.830 --> 28:41.190
I remember

28:41.880 --> 28:45.540
someone playing Go with me
from a distance in the Fengyu Pavilion.

28:45.780 --> 28:47.110
Our moves went back and forth,

28:47.110 --> 28:49.240
breaking stalemates again and again.

28:53.640 --> 28:55.160
I also have a friend

28:55.160 --> 28:56.420
who is excellent at Go.

28:57.590 --> 28:58.720
But...

28:58.720 --> 29:00.000
we have never met.

29:00.480 --> 29:01.610
What a coincidence.

29:02.920 --> 29:03.920
Perhaps...

29:04.830 --> 29:06.590
I'll be able to meet him soon.

29:16.860 --> 29:17.520
Please.

29:45.620 --> 29:48.210
Do you know why I came back?

29:58.720 --> 29:59.980
The road ahead is long.

30:00.210 --> 30:03.610
I only wish for Your Highness
to return to the capital safely.

30:07.680 --> 30:09.340
You knew my identity long ago?

30:11.080 --> 30:14.210
I only found out your identity
the day before yesterday.

30:15.760 --> 30:17.890
When you first arrived at the academy,

30:18.240 --> 30:20.530
I noticed that you were a woman.

30:21.640 --> 30:22.640
Who is An Xu?

30:23.640 --> 30:24.480
An Xu.

30:24.720 --> 30:25.720
He's calling you.

30:26.680 --> 30:27.680
Mr. An.

30:28.680 --> 30:31.050
You look so outstanding,

30:30.220 --> 30:31.860
♪ I just don't want to ♪

30:31.270 --> 30:32.750
magnificent,

30:32.480 --> 30:33.330
♪ Keep weighing every word ♪

30:33.350 --> 30:35.520
♪ And hiding in time in silence ♪

30:33.750 --> 30:35.270
and distinguished.

30:36.440 --> 30:37.840
I just didn't expect

30:36.510 --> 30:38.270
♪ It's not that I don't believe in karma ♪

30:38.750 --> 30:40.300
that you were actually
the current Princess Royal.

30:38.930 --> 30:41.090
♪ That I'm being stubborn ♪

30:42.810 --> 30:44.560
♪ Some endings have long been ♪

30:44.830 --> 30:47.090
I came to this academy for someone.

30:45.150 --> 30:46.420
♪ Weathered through a thousand years ♪

30:46.450 --> 30:48.440
♪ Traced by those who come after ♪

30:49.050 --> 30:50.990
♪ Compared to fading away in sorrow ♪

30:51.490 --> 30:53.720
♪ I'd rather fight ♪

30:54.500 --> 30:57.200
♪ Life's bitterness ♪

30:57.690 --> 31:00.090
♪ Comes from love ♪

31:00.900 --> 31:03.460
♪ Love, yet so hard to hold ♪

31:03.930 --> 31:06.710
♪ Like holing a torch in the wilderness ♪

31:05.160 --> 31:08.160
That the Princess Royal favors our academy

31:07.370 --> 31:09.530
♪ Time sings a mournful song ♪

31:08.180 --> 31:10.250
is an honor for us all.

31:10.240 --> 31:12.580
♪ Gathered little yet parted often ♪

31:13.400 --> 31:16.430
♪ Just as tears fall into the long river ♪

31:16.820 --> 31:20.630
This is the Go manual
I copied for you as I promised,

31:16.870 --> 31:21.810
♪ I must dive into the starry stream ♪

31:21.880 --> 31:23.030
"The Mystery of Qi."

31:23.960 --> 31:24.630
♪ Don't mind me ♪

31:24.650 --> 31:25.640
♪ Everything has happened ♪

31:24.990 --> 31:27.300
I'm giving it to you now

31:26.000 --> 31:29.280
♪ A thousand years from now
no one's blood will remain warm ♪

31:28.100 --> 31:29.380
as a parting gift.

31:30.120 --> 31:32.020
♪ Let them laugh and mock ♪

31:32.590 --> 31:35.680
♪ I just want you to remember me ♪

31:36.480 --> 31:37.050
♪ Don't care about ♪

31:37.070 --> 31:38.200
♪ Leaving a name in history ♪

31:38.880 --> 31:41.990
♪ I only want to leave a mark
in your life ♪

31:42.790 --> 31:44.180
♪ I will let go ♪

31:45.220 --> 31:48.460
♪ After taking this one last gamble ♪

31:49.090 --> 31:49.730
♪ Don't mind ♪

31:49.750 --> 31:50.940
♪ The carved stones or constellations ♪

31:51.500 --> 31:54.390
♪ I'll cast all karma behind me ♪

31:55.370 --> 31:57.280
♪ Playing war with the lords ♪

31:57.770 --> 32:01.400
♪ Leaving no trace of fate ♪

32:19.140 --> 32:20.900
Headmaster. Headmaster.

32:24.750 --> 32:27.030
It is so late. Why are you still up?

32:28.440 --> 32:30.790
An asked me to pass this letter to you.

32:51.390 --> 32:52.560
So it was her.

32:59.950 --> 33:01.090
In this game of Go,

33:03.710 --> 33:06.030
I was utterly crushed.

33:18.660 --> 33:21.840
[Composed]

33:24.160 --> 33:25.480
Your Highness.

33:26.300 --> 33:29.300
Since Princess Royal
returned from the river region,

33:29.350 --> 33:31.730
she has stayed behind closed doors

33:32.150 --> 33:34.790
and barely touched her meals.

33:35.510 --> 33:37.930
It seems Gongsun Yin has no affection

33:38.030 --> 33:40.570
for the Princess Royal.

33:41.350 --> 33:43.070
If she knows,

33:43.070 --> 33:45.200
she would be heartbroken.

33:45.640 --> 33:48.070
The Gongsun family
even sent a personal letter,

33:48.070 --> 33:49.400
sincere in their words.

33:50.640 --> 33:52.870
I was a little surprised.

33:52.960 --> 33:56.300
But with Her Highness's temperament,

33:56.440 --> 33:58.950
she probably won't give up easily.

34:04.950 --> 34:06.710
Shu is still young

34:05.430 --> 34:09.230
[Consort Dowager An, Mother of Qi Shu]

34:06.730 --> 34:09.060
and doesn't understand
all the complexities.

34:09.060 --> 34:10.960
The Gongsun family may have prestige,

34:10.960 --> 34:12.920
but after all,
they are not a suitable match.

34:12.920 --> 34:14.940
You are right, Your Highness.

34:15.550 --> 34:18.960
How should we persuade Her Highness?

34:19.920 --> 34:22.780
Grand Tutor Li
has a reputation for virtue in court.

34:23.219 --> 34:25.310
His eldest grandson, Li Huai'an,

34:25.340 --> 34:27.940
is said to have achieved much
in the Northwest.

34:28.570 --> 34:30.690
He's also a man of great appearance

34:31.550 --> 34:33.800
and could be considered a suitable match.

34:33.800 --> 34:36.030
Perhaps we should find a chance

34:36.330 --> 34:38.230
and arrange a meeting between him and Shu.

34:38.230 --> 34:40.560
I'll make the arrangements immediately.

34:45.880 --> 34:46.630
Shu,

34:47.710 --> 34:49.440
don't blame me for being harsh.

34:49.760 --> 34:51.150
No matter how unwilling you are now,

34:51.150 --> 34:53.010
you'll understand in the future.

34:57.530 --> 35:02.000
[Three days later]

35:11.000 --> 35:12.630
A blind date with the Princess Royal?

35:12.630 --> 35:13.960
It seems my grandfather

35:14.230 --> 35:17.030
is still obsessed with his rivalry
against Wei Yan

35:17.360 --> 35:19.320
and wants to help me secure a footing

35:19.320 --> 35:20.780
among the royal nobility.

35:22.400 --> 35:23.480
In the end,

35:24.960 --> 35:27.320
it's just party disputes.

35:28.590 --> 35:29.800
It brings no benefit

35:30.280 --> 35:31.880
to the stability of the state

35:31.960 --> 35:33.560
or the welfare of the people.

35:36.230 --> 35:37.000
My Lord.

35:38.110 --> 35:39.960
The Grand Tutor is your grandfather.

35:39.960 --> 35:41.690
You should try to persuade him.

35:43.440 --> 35:44.770
I may be short-sighted,

35:45.630 --> 35:47.260
but all these years at the border,

35:47.260 --> 35:51.730
[To my grandson, Huai'an]

35:47.950 --> 35:50.680
whether it was General He
or the Marquis of Wu'an,

35:50.920 --> 35:52.510
although they belong to the Wei faction,

35:52.510 --> 35:53.840
they were fearless in battle

35:53.840 --> 35:55.760
and good men who defended the border.

35:55.760 --> 35:57.360
Grandfather has given orders.

35:57.360 --> 35:59.020
I have no choice but to go back.

36:00.590 --> 36:01.480
Fortunately,

36:02.770 --> 36:04.770
the Marquis of Wu'an is still alive.

36:06.280 --> 36:07.620
As long as he is here,

36:08.400 --> 36:10.330
the Northwest will remain stable.

36:17.630 --> 36:19.670
Dry weather!

36:19.620 --> 36:23.620
[Tofu]

36:20.510 --> 36:23.480
Beware of fire!

36:31.800 --> 36:33.460
Lin'an is indeed a nice place.

36:35.010 --> 36:36.700
If I can settle down one day,

36:38.730 --> 36:39.920
I'd also like to live such a

36:39.920 --> 36:41.980
carefree life like a drifting cloud.

37:06.360 --> 37:08.510
Did Lord Li really return to the Capital?

37:08.510 --> 37:10.320
I met him on my way home.

37:10.960 --> 37:13.270
He said now that the matter with Guo
has been resolved,

37:13.270 --> 37:14.840
he must go back to Lucheng
to report first,

37:14.840 --> 37:16.100
then go to the Capital.

37:26.660 --> 37:27.790
What else did he say?

37:28.480 --> 37:30.810
He asked when my parents arrived in Lin'an

37:30.960 --> 37:33.270
and if I remember what happened
16 years ago.

37:33.270 --> 37:34.760
I was only 2 then.

37:34.840 --> 37:36.300
How could I remember that?

37:36.630 --> 37:38.830
I need to ask my grandfather about that.

37:40.840 --> 37:43.330
Changning, we have roasted chestnuts.

37:43.920 --> 37:46.480
Changyu, Zheng, look who's back.

37:46.550 --> 37:52.000
[Be a Good Person]

37:49.520 --> 37:51.560
Zheng didn't lie to me.

37:51.590 --> 37:53.340
The falcon is really back.

37:56.320 --> 37:58.050
You're so good at taming birds?

37:58.510 --> 38:01.510
Maybe you just fed it too well,

38:01.590 --> 38:03.190
so it couldn't bear to leave.

38:03.550 --> 38:04.840
Is it that greedy?

38:06.630 --> 38:08.230
Since you know how to come home,

38:08.230 --> 38:10.620
I won't lock you in the cage anymore.

38:10.990 --> 38:12.000
You can be free.

38:25.320 --> 38:26.800
It's just like me.

38:26.880 --> 38:29.150
Was it born of my mother too?

38:29.170 --> 38:30.020
Yes.

38:30.510 --> 38:32.440
Raising it also needs a lot of food.

38:35.550 --> 38:36.150
Here.

38:46.880 --> 38:49.480
The dream in the Fengyu Pavilion
has ended.

38:51.960 --> 38:53.150
Baffling.

38:58.400 --> 38:59.260
Your Lordship,

38:59.480 --> 39:02.080
that rascal Li Huai'an
has really left Lin'an.

39:02.110 --> 39:04.770
Mr. Gongsun's diversion tactic
really worked.

39:06.440 --> 39:07.510
I'm also curious about

39:07.510 --> 39:09.190
what tricks that brat used.

39:09.230 --> 39:09.840
By the way,

39:10.110 --> 39:12.150
at the border
between Yanzhou and Chongzhou,

39:12.150 --> 39:13.800
bandits have been raiding military grain.

39:13.800 --> 39:15.230
Wei Xuan was furious this time

39:15.230 --> 39:17.830
and ordered them
to be wiped out within 10 days.

39:19.240 --> 39:20.820
What kind of bandits have a death wish

39:20.820 --> 39:23.000
to repeatedly
rob government grain convoys?

39:23.000 --> 39:25.200
It must be Prince Changxin behind this.

39:27.280 --> 39:28.630
That fool Wei Xuan

39:29.300 --> 39:31.100
is about to fall into their trap.

39:32.280 --> 39:34.280
Keep monitoring all recent intelligence

39:34.280 --> 39:35.510
about the grain.

39:36.070 --> 39:36.670
Yes.

39:37.110 --> 39:37.710
Your Lordship,

39:37.710 --> 39:39.400
it's late. You should head back and rest

39:39.400 --> 39:40.930
before the Marchioness...

39:41.880 --> 39:43.320
be-becomes suspicious.

39:51.850 --> 39:54.110
My stupid mouth ran faster than my brain.

39:54.130 --> 39:55.590
I blurted out my thoughts.

39:56.070 --> 39:56.880
Let's go.

40:10.520 --> 40:14.900
[Enjoy Yourself]

40:17.780 --> 40:18.510
Manager.

40:18.880 --> 40:20.190
Manager Zhao from the Lin'an Rice Shop

40:20.190 --> 40:21.440
booked a private room on the second floor

40:21.440 --> 40:22.280
to entertain an important guest.

40:22.280 --> 40:22.960
Look,

40:23.630 --> 40:26.150
he ordered our best wine and dishes.

40:27.840 --> 40:29.230
Okay, I got it.

40:29.230 --> 40:30.110
Go get things ready.

40:30.110 --> 40:31.110
I'll go up to greet them in a moment.

40:31.110 --> 40:31.670
Alright.

40:38.190 --> 40:39.690
[Heaven-class]

40:41.190 --> 40:42.510
Manager Zhao.

40:43.320 --> 40:45.880
Taking time out of your busy schedule
to visit Yixiang Restaurant,

40:45.880 --> 40:47.840
it's truly an honor for us.

40:48.490 --> 40:52.210
[Zhao Xun, Manager of Lin'an Rice Shop]

40:49.320 --> 40:50.990
Manager Yu, you're too polite.

40:50.990 --> 40:52.390
How is business today?

40:53.710 --> 40:55.780
Business is good, of course.

41:05.510 --> 41:07.710
May I ask who this guest is?

41:08.550 --> 41:10.590
This is a rice merchant from the Capital,

41:10.590 --> 41:11.510
Mr. Qi.

41:11.850 --> 41:14.780
[Qi Min]

41:12.000 --> 41:14.400
He's here
to discuss some business with me.

41:15.440 --> 41:17.840
So you are a distinguished guest
from afar.

41:18.230 --> 41:20.490
I hope the food and wine suit your tastes.

41:20.630 --> 41:21.710
If you need anything,

41:21.710 --> 41:23.040
please just let me know.

41:24.630 --> 41:26.430
The food and wine are excellent.

41:27.590 --> 41:30.140
Especially this Snow Bun Soup.

41:31.840 --> 41:33.890
This is our signature dish.

41:35.280 --> 41:36.510
To serve such an distinguished guest

41:36.510 --> 41:37.850
is my honor.

41:38.320 --> 41:40.230
Let me propose a toast to you.

42:12.880 --> 42:14.960
Let me know if you need anything else.

42:15.150 --> 42:16.550
Manager Yu, please wait.

42:17.070 --> 42:18.630
Mr. Qi, you might not know,

42:19.190 --> 42:22.050
but I haven't been
running a shop in Lin'an for long.

42:22.370 --> 42:24.830
But Manager Yu has been in business
for years

42:24.960 --> 42:26.820
and knows the local network best.

42:27.030 --> 42:29.180
If you have any business ideas,

42:29.760 --> 42:32.710
you could ask Manager Yu for advice.

42:37.280 --> 42:40.000
What business are you planning, sir?

42:40.150 --> 42:42.210
I am not familiar with the rice trade.

42:42.760 --> 42:45.150
But if you want
to collaborate with someone,

42:45.150 --> 42:47.210
I can introduce you to a few managers.

42:49.280 --> 42:51.340
Manager Yu, you are very experienced

42:51.350 --> 42:52.550
in receiving guests.

42:53.920 --> 42:56.250
It seems you really do know
a lot of people.

43:03.800 --> 43:05.440
Our shop serves guests from all over.

43:05.440 --> 43:07.210
We believe harmony brings wealth.

43:07.210 --> 43:08.290
In business,

43:08.510 --> 43:10.920
it's always good to know more people.

43:12.110 --> 43:13.340
It's all for business.

43:13.340 --> 43:14.510
I understand.

43:27.400 --> 43:29.070
Please enjoy yourselves.

43:29.070 --> 43:31.010
I will go attend to other guests.

43:31.030 --> 43:32.150
Please go ahead, Manager Yu.
